The Fulbright Application Process
#####################################
Visit the site here: `Fulbright Website <https://us.fulbrightonline.org>`_
.. image:: logo.png
  :width: 400
  :alt: Fulbright Logo
The following site aims to give an overview and procedures for applying for a U.S. Fulbright Scholarhsip. 

In this site you will find:

#. App Navigation
#. Timelines
#. Essay Guides
#. Language Prep
#. Action Lists

By the end you will be able to:

* Know the right steps to take to start your application
* Successfully navigate the application portal
* Put your best foot forward!

