=========  ========  ======= 
 Fulbright Timeline
----------------------------
 Date      Task      Product
=========  ========  =======
June       False     False 
July       False     True 
September  True      True 
October    True      True 
=========  ========  =======

The key to a successful application to thoughtul preparation at the right times.
 
